com.camerontec.catalys.server.configuration

Interface IMutableConfigurationWithCustomAttributes

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, IConfiguration, IMutableConfiguration, IRegisterable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CustomConnectionConfiguration, CustomMarketDataServiceConfiguration, CustomMessageFactoryConfiguration, CustomMessageProcessorConfiguration, CustomMonitorConfiguration, CustomPersisterConfiguration, CustomSelectorConfiguration, CustomServiceConfiguration, SessionManagerConfiguration

    public interface IMutableConfigurationWithCustomAttributes
extends IMutableConfiguration
    'Custom attributes' are attributes which are not declared in our DTD but which the custom added to a modified DTD)

    WARNING classes implementing this interface should override IConfiguration.getConfigurationAsProperties() to include the custom attributes
